nodes.title: howto
widgets_values:
NAVIGATION
ALT+C (OPT+C) to open/collapse nodes.
` 1 2 3 4 keys to switch between proofing and over view 
CTRL-B to bypass a node.

STEP BY STEP
1 ‚≠ïPrompt from +T5X3 and - "Convert Input" on G+ or L+ to write individual prompts.
2 ‚≠ïParameters, set in Selector, Seed, Load ‚ü∑. default_scale gets filename number
3 ‚≠ïCheckpoint file, set 1(any) or 2(XL). Stages share models & focus their own.
4 ‚≠ïLoadVAE, ensure Stage checkpoint matches, or bypass for ckpt with built-in vae.
5 ‚≠ïSave path and filename..
6 ‚≠ïI/O groups disable/enable unused. Run one Stage at a time on old hardware.
7 queue!
NOTES
- Collapse nodes before mute/bypass buttons. Nodes crossing groups causes issues.
- 'Last Queued' empties on browser refresh
- ‚≠ïLoadLatent or LoadLmage take priority over Empty Latent unless bypassed
- In Load‚ü∑, set default as the x# from the file name
- Enable interposer when converting between v1.5/xl/etc. models
- To adjust group positions, raise logo window from bottom right corner
- Each image chimes & notifies browser by default. snake alertsICON KEY
